==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: lullaby
<hw>lull"a*by</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[From <er>Lull</er>,
<pos>v. t.</pos> ]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A song to quiet babes or lull
them to sleep; that which quiets.</def> <rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Hence: Good night; good-by.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Luller</ent>⟦br⟧
